Here's how you dance the Monstrosity. Stand with your feet together.
Now, move your left foot weird to the side. Now stamp your
right foot 8 times and put your hands on your partner's
cats . Next, you both pol slowly to the right and bend
your jj backward. For the next eight counts,
both of you jjj b to the left. Next, you and
your partner stand back to back and wiggle your n and
slap your tyui together. Don't forget to keep stamping
your right foot. Now, face your partner again, put your rxy
together and shout, " u !" Now, h backward
and repeat the whole thing b times. If you feel that you can't
learn this dance, you can always  the next one out.
